author: Kam Dhillon
title: Here’s What Tokyo Wore to Supreme’s Lacoste Drop
text:
Visit the original post to see all 20 images from this gallery. 
Location: Tokyo, Japan
Season: Spring/Summer 2017
Key Looks: The camo surgical mask (slide #13), that perfectly oversized sweatshirt (slide #9), and an expert lesson in spring-time layering (slide #14).
Editor’s Notes: We snapped Tokyo’s streetwear aficionados lining up to cop some coveted pieces from Supreme’s latest collaboration with Lacoste, and as expected, the crowd came out in plenty of the Supreme’s greatest hits.
Now you’ve seen the best street style from Tokyo, check out what London’s streetwear set wore to Supreme x Lacoste SS17’s drop.
